node.text:
Thank you to @shobabi for creating this video for us! #sudio #sudiomoments
Dancing with- @francardenas_
@javilove1 @liiljohnjohn 🎥- @thealantan_ @cfpo77
Edited by- @thealantan_
Animated by- @jay_hemrajani

Weekends always seem to go by so fast! Can you believe it's already Saturday?😬 What are your plans?⁠
⁠
#sudio #shapingsound #ett-anthracite @wasabiitooo

Remember our best selling model, Tolv? Well, say hello to the new and improved T2 model🤩

Sudio T2 is designed for more life. With a brand new redesign, we’ve even added Jade, the latest addition to our popping new colour selection.

✔️Active noise cancellation means a deeper listen without interruption
✔️Beamforming microphones control environmental noise for clearer calls
✔️Dynamic driver delivers crisp, uncompromising sound.

Please check out our official website http://sudio.com for more details! Tell us what you think about T2 in the comment section below ⬇️

#sudio #shapingsound #t2-jade

node.text:
Compact, yet powerful! The Nio model has fierce features that you'll want to try for yourself:⁠
-20hrs of total play time⁠
-Sweat Resistant⁠
-10meter range⁠
⁠
Check them out at Sudio.com to read the full list of features offered🌱⁠
⁠
#sudio #shapingsound #nio-white @josefinsinredniing

We want to get to know you and see what you’re doing with your Sudio products! Show us how you shape your sound with Sudio products using #sudio and #shapingsound for a chance to get featured. Visit our website to find your favorites and local stores. ⁠
⁠
#sudio #shapingsound #tolv-black @huisjenn
